HEADWORD: Anguillan
<hw>Anguillan</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a native or inhabitant
of the island of Anguilla in the West Indies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anguillan</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Anguillan
<hw>Anguillan</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>of or pertaining to
